{"tid":1655971,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"十一月區會啦 係咪又想比建制班仆街贏？","createTime":"2019-10-15T10:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T12:10:28.000Z","uid":109531,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8f2a16bf0d85ef4006782c08b5b9c8f9554d6127","tid":1655971,"uid":109531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:40:47.000Z","msg":"成日講一票不投民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係啦 咁我地真係唔投比民建聯啦<br />\n但係即使我地投比其他黨派嘅人都好<br />\n票數咁散 佢地點入到區會呀？ 加上根本唔知投比邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地係咪差唔多係時候有個共識傾下十八區我地分別要投比邊個候選人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有共識後就靠十八區嘅大家谷恆所有票比我地要揀嘅候選人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細佬自問真係熟唔晒十八區嘅情況<br />\n希望會有熱心手足幫手整合各區情況！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光黎區會 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">票投民建聯 香港玩撚完</span></span>"},{"pid":"5517808df7914035e04386a38708566ccb2bfc9f","tid":1655971,"uid":109531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:41:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5835bef0828d1603c410bb2cc10abb8a5b63f48f","tid":1655971,"uid":109531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:41:20.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"3293a0063ca1610ee98996687a4de5458d705637","tid":1655971,"uid":109531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:42:09.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"c5011e6632c3ae978cf61da22b5d3f06e027b7a8","tid":1655971,"uid":109531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:42:48.000Z","msg":"Hello"},{"pid":"38a9983fb23866783bc5a96fef08d83bdb162414","tid":1655971,"uid":109531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:42:59.000Z","msg":"好撚重要呀！"},{"pid":"9eccd087e7c4dd490f5fc8ee5aeb3